AMAPHOYISA athungatha abasolwa ababulale izithandani ngokuzishaya  eShayamoya KwaMpumuza, ngaphandle kwaseMgungundlovu ngoba bezisola ngokweba. UNksz Londeka Mvelase noMnuz Mxolisi Mchunu, kuthiwa bashaywe ngamalungu omphakathi, baze bafa ngeSonto. Izithandani bezihlala ndawonye. Kuthiwa bezisolwa ngokweba imali elinganiselwa kuR2 500 neselula kamakhelwane. Isolezwe lithole ukuthi laba kwale ngisho sebecela uxolo kabazange bayekwe ukushaywa, bakhandwa nangamatshe. Kuthiwa bekukhona abesifazane nabesilisa ngesikhathi beshaywa. Ikhansela lakule ndawo, uNkk Jabu Zondo, lihambele kule ndawo izolo ukuzokhuza ngokwenzekile. Likhuluma neSolezwe, lithe yize bebesolwa ngokweba kodwa bekungamele babulawe. “Sengibuya khona emphakathini. Kukhona ukuthi siyakhala ngobugebengu, buyasihlupha impela kule ndawo, yize kunjalo kodwa akuvumelekile ukuba umphakathi uziphindiselele. Kumele ubize amaphoyisa kube yiwona abopha abantu abonayo. Ngolwazi engilutholile, abasolwa bebesolwa ngokuntshontsha endaweni. Uzinzo lukhona endaweni njengamanje, kunokuthula. Umfana akuyena owendawo, owesifazane ngowakhona endaweni. Ngisazofuna umndeni wakhe, bese siyahlangana nawo kusasa (namhlanje) sikhulume ngalolu daba,” kusho uNkk Ngubo. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala uthe kuvulwe amacala amabili okubulala,  amaphoyisa asathungatha abasolwa.  Imizamo yeSolezwe yokuthola imindeni yababulewe kayizange iphumelele izolo ngoba izinombolo zabo bezingatholakali, kwaze kwashaya isikhathi sokushicilela. 